<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>我们可是专业的 无论做出什么事都要收回债务</b></font>

128
00:07:45,960 --> 00:07:48,750
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>开司你的父亲 以前是个公务员吧</b></font>

129
00:07:50,290 --> 00:07:55,300
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>而且现在虽然没有父亲 母亲还在努力地工作挣钱</b></font>

130
00:07:56,010 --> 00:07:56,840
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>你这混蛋</b></font>

131
00:07:57,300 --> 00:07:58,050
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>开司</b></font>

132
00:08:02,560 --> 00:08:06,480
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>这不是我的本意 这不是我的本意啊</b></font>

133
00:08:06,940 --> 00:08:09,980
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>我也不想看到你们家人间互相辱骂的场面</b></font>

134
00:08:11,060 --> 00:08:13,280
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>坐下来 我们进入正题吧</b></font>

135
00:08:13,650 --> 00:08:14,280
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>正题?</b></font>

136
00:08:14,440 --> 00:08:18,160
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>没错 我接下来要说的 才是我的本意</b></font>

137
00:08:21,280 --> 00:08:24,120
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>一个月后 在晴海码头会有一艘船出航</b></font>

138
00:08:24,410 --> 00:08:26,660
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>现在我正在征募愿意搭乘这艘船的参加者</b></font>

139
00:08:27,830 --> 00:08:33,210
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>只要能在那船上熬过一晚 你的债一笔勾销</b></font>

140
00:08:33,420 --> 00:08:34,550
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>哎? 勾销</b></font>

141
00:08:34,840 --> 00:08:38,380
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>不仅如此 还有可能赚上一千万甚至两千万</b></font>

142
00:08:39,010 --> 00:08:40,470
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>这...这是</b></font>

143
00:08:41,010 --> 00:08:42,260
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>赌博</b></font>

144
00:08:43,350 --> 00:08:45,810
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>把像你这样走投无路的负债人聚集起来</b></font>

145
00:08:45,870 --> 00:08:48,000
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>让你们进行仅限一夜的赌博</b></font>

146
00:08:48,520 --> 00:08:52,560
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>如果在那船上输掉的话 债务会变得更高</b></font>

147
00:08:52,860 --> 00:08:56,400
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>会被带去某个地方 至少也要强制劳动个一两年</b></font>

148
00:08:56,940 --> 00:08:58,490
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>无法回到日本</b></font>

149
00:08:59,450 --> 00:09:04,120
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>但是每次也都有好几个赚到大钱下船的人</b></font>

150
00:09:04,910 --> 00:09:07,830
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>开司 你上船吧</b></font>

151
00:09:09,540 --> 00:09:12,880
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>上船熬过去 清掉一身债再回来</b></font>

152
00:09:15,670 --> 00:09:16,630
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>赢了的话就一笔勾销</b></font>

153
00:09:17,380 --> 00:09:18,090
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>嗯</b></font>

154
00:09:23,300 --> 00:09:25,600
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>像你这样的人渣的最后一战</b></font>

155
00:09:26,350 --> 00:09:29,480
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>被各自的欲望所驱使着聚集到一起的人渣们</b></font>

156
00:09:29,810 --> 00:09:32,690
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>徘徊在鬼门关前的修罗之船</b></font>

157
00:09:33,150 --> 00:09:36,860
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>它的名字叫作希望号 希望之船</b></font>

158
00:09:45,910 --> 00:09:47,240
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>下定决心了吗</b></font>

159
00:09:48,950 --> 00:09:50,370
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>可以问两个问题吗</b></font>

160
00:09:51,120 --> 00:09:51,700
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>嗯?</b></font>

161
00:09:52,620 --> 00:09:54,960
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>一是在船上将进行哪一种赌博</b></font>

162
00:09:55,830 --> 00:09:59,960
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>二是输了的话要强制劳动 具体会做些什么</b></font>

163
00:10:00,380 --> 00:10:03,050
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>很遗憾 这两个问题都无法回答</b></font>

164
00:10:03,300 --> 00:10:04,090
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>怎么会...</b></font>

165
00:10:04,340 --> 00:10:07,640
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>听我说 如果告诉你怎么赌的话</b></font>

166
00:10:08,140 --> 00:10:11,470
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>越早决定参加的人越有利吧</b></font>

167
00:10:12,680 --> 00:10:14,980
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>还有 关于输了的时候的处分</b></font>

168
00:10:15,390 --> 00:10:17,730
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>这件事我也不清楚</b></font>

169
00:10:18,520 --> 00:10:19,230
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>你不清楚?</b></font>

170
00:10:19,820 --> 00:10:21,570
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>但是 不用担心</b></font>

171
00:10:22,230 --> 00:10:27,450
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>这艘游轮的目的 本质在于救济负债者</b></font>

172
00:10:27,700 --> 00:10:28,320
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>救济?</b></font>

173
00:10:29,530 --> 00:10:32,240
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>策划这次游轮之旅并进行赞助的是</b></font>

174
00:10:32,490 --> 00:10:36,370
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>名字人尽皆知的某大金融公司</b></font>

175
00:10:37,000 --> 00:10:40,920
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>赞助商绝不会有“利用这艘船捞一笔”那种廉价的想法</b></font>

176
00:10:41,550 --> 00:10:45,800
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>这次的赌博 并不是像赌场里进行的那种一样</b></font>

177
00:10:46,170 --> 00:10:48,470
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>说到底只是参加者之间的得失</b></font>

178
00:10:48,970 --> 00:10:49,970
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>参加者之间?</b></font>

179
00:10:50,430 --> 00:10:55,100
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>没错 而结果 每一次都有一半的人可以下船</b></font>

180
00:10:55,430 --> 00:10:56,180
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>居然有一半?</b></font>

181
00:10:57,230 --> 00:10:58,940
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>赢的话 借款就一笔勾销</b></font>

182
00:10:59,520 --> 00:11:01,110
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>这毫无疑问是救济</b></font>

183
00:11:01,360 --> 00:11:06,190
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>即使输了 比起长久受借款困扰生活下去</b></font>

184
00:11:06,570 --> 00:11:10,490
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>过一两年艰苦生活 集中把债还了</b></font>

185
00:11:10,990 --> 00:11:14,290
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>就此从借款中解放 要幸福的多吧</b></font>

186
00:11:14,540 --> 00:11:15,750
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>你不这么认为吧</b></font>

187
00:11:16,290 --> 00:11:18,330
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>嗯 确实如此</b></font>

188
00:11:19,120 --> 00:11:24,550
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>我呢 觉得你能参加这游轮之行是一种幸运</b></font>

189
00:11:25,420 --> 00:11:28,180
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>你每天的生活就像垃圾一样吧</b></font>

190
00:11:28,680 --> 00:11:31,140
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>没有精神 自甘堕落 不具生产力</b></font>

191
00:11:32,470 --> 00:11:33,060
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>是吧</b></font>

192
00:11:34,430 --> 00:11:35,310
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>算是吧</b></font>

193
00:11:35,810 --> 00:11:37,930
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>你知道为什么会变成这样吗</b></font>

194
00:11:38,230 --> 00:11:38,890
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>不...</b></font>

195
00:11:39,390 --> 00:11:41,400
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>因为你没有钱花</b></font>

196
00:11:42,270 --> 00:11:42,860
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>钱?</b></font>

197
00:11:43,230 --> 00:11:47,110
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>没错 因为你没钱 所以每天都活得不真实</b></font>

198
00:11:47,690 --> 00:11:51,280
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>比如说打篮球时球篮在百米上空</b></font>

199
00:11:51,660 --> 00:11:53,830
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>谁都不会想要去投篮的</b></font>

200
00:11:54,870 --> 00:11:58,500
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>现在的你就是对这种无法触及的目标感到厌烦了</b></font>

201
00:11:59,460 --> 00:12:03,250
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>就算有想要的东西 也都在柜台的里面</b></font>

202
00:12:03,630 --> 00:12:04,960
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>你是构不着的</b></font>

203
00:12:05,300 --> 00:12:09,720
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>这种买不起东西的压力 使你丧失了霸气</b></font>

204
00:12:09,760 --> 00:12:12,050
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>扼杀了你真实的心情</b></font>

205
00:12:12,550 --> 00:12:14,850
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>你经常对外国车展开恶作剧吧</b></font>

206
00:12:15,260 --> 00:12:17,470
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>那种行为就是典型的象征</b></font>

207
00:12:17,930 --> 00:12:21,400
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>明明想要外国车 但甚至不敢去想如何将其占为己有</b></font>

208
00:12:21,980 --> 00:12:25,860
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>一开始就已经放弃 做一些小家子气的恶作剧而自我满足</b></font>

209
00:12:26,230 --> 00:12:29,190
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>如果你有一千万在手你还会做那种事吗</b></font>

210
00:12:30,280 --> 00:12:31,240
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>不会的吧</b></font>

211
00:12:32,110 --> 00:12:33,530
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>这次也是一样</b></font>

212
00:12:34,160 --> 00:12:36,950
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>对于这么好的救济机会 也毫不关心</b></font>

213
00:12:37,490 --> 00:12:39,620
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>这就是你已经输惯了的证明</b></font>

214
00:12:40,870 --> 00:12:45,040
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>这次的游轮之行是可以一扫你输惯了的习性的好机会</b></font>

215
00:12:45,710 --> 00:12:51,130
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>我说开司啊 获胜赚大钱 改变人生吧</b></font>

216
00:12:53,720 --> 00:12:56,350
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>老大 吉居先生的电话</b></font>

217
00:13:02,100 --> 00:13:03,190
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>您好 我是远藤</b></font>

218
00:13:05,940 --> 00:13:10,820
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>的确我...该怎么说...已经斗争了很久</b></font>

219
00:13:11,860 --> 00:13:15,620
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>开司 只剩两个位子了</b></font>

220
00:13:17,330 --> 00:13:22,460
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>这次游轮之旅的位子 不光是我一个人在分派的啦</b></font>

221
00:13:24,250 --> 00:13:25,830
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>喂 这里是远藤金融</b></font>

222
00:13:26,750 --> 00:13:31,170
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>两个位子? 只剩两个位子...即使这么说也</b></font>

223
00:13:33,800 --> 00:13:36,720
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>开司 很遗憾</b></font>

224
00:13:37,600 --> 00:13:38,430
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>没有了</b></font>

225
00:13:38,470 --> 00:13:44,600
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>哎? 等等...能不能再想想办法</b></font>

226
00:13:45,150 --> 00:13:48,360
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>什么? 你想参加了吗</b></font>

227
00:13:49,150 --> 00:13:51,190
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>嗯 如果非要我选的话...</b></font>

228
00:13:52,740 --> 00:13:55,280
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>真是的...等一下...我打过去问问</b></font>

229
00:13:57,070 --> 00:13:57,870
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>麻烦你了</b></font>

230
00:13:59,080 --> 00:14:04,120
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>吉居先生 我是远藤 其实是那个...</b></font>

231
00:14:04,360 --> 00:14:07,530
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>嗯 是的 没错</b></font>

232
00:14:08,340 --> 00:14:09,290
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>拜托了</b></font>

233
00:14:11,880 --> 00:14:15,340
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>成功说服了 说是会增加一个位子</b></font>

234
00:14:16,300 --> 00:14:17,260
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>真的吗</b></font>

235
00:14:17,590 --> 00:14:20,810
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>那么 就立刻在这协议上签字并按上手印吧</b></font>

236
00:14:23,060 --> 00:14:25,060
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>就这样 开司</b></font>

237
00:14:25,880 --> 00:14:26,590
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>辛苦了</b></font>

238
00:14:28,060 --> 00:14:28,940
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>订下了契约</b></font>

239
00:14:31,690 --> 00:14:34,740
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>真是轻易中计了呢 只靠一个手机电话</b></font>

240
00:14:35,200 --> 00:14:39,160
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>把还在迷茫的人逼上绝路 放高利贷时的常用手段吧</b></font>

241
00:14:39,740 --> 00:14:43,910
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>这种莫名其妙的游轮怎么可能会人满为患嘛</b></font>

242
00:14:44,500 --> 00:14:48,380
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>真要说的话 他是下不了船的那一类人</b></font>

243
00:14:48,540 --> 00:14:50,250
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>这个嘛 他当然不行了</b></font>

244
00:14:50,330 --> 00:14:54,540
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>你想想 刚才我打说服游轮方面的假电话时</b></font>

245
00:14:54,920 --> 00:14:58,340
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>他可能以为我是个好人呢</b></font>

246
00:14:58,470 --> 00:14:59,680
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>好人吗</b></font>

